Description: Cylinder seal of brown steatite: perforated through the centre and slightly broken at one end. The incised inscription is written in two rectangular frames.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 110, abb. 578; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1166.
Acquisition name: Purchased from: Rev George Denis Nash
